Sentencas: We report on the synthesis of electrode layers by Pulsed Laser Deposition technique.
Titulo: Structural investigations on electrodes - electrolytes systems for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell applications

Sentencas: We selected Nickel Oxide-8Yttria-Stabilized Zirconia as anode, La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3-delta perovskite material as cathode, and Yttria doped (Ceria-alpha Alumina) as electrolyte.
Titulo: Structural investigations on electrodes - electrolytes systems for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell applications

Sentencas: We studied electrode structure (average grain size, porosity, and grain shape), the deposition uniformity and electrode-electrolyte interfaces.
Titulo: Structural investigations on electrodes - electrolytes systems for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell applications

Sentencas: The electrodes were investigated in terms of morphology (Scanning Electron Microscopy) and composition (Energy Dispersive X-ray Spectroscopy).
Titulo: Structural investigations on electrodes - electrolytes systems for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell applications

Sentencas: The initial powder and the synthesized cathodes have been investigated superficially and in bulk by Mossbauer spectroscopy, in order to detect and analyse local properties.
Titulo: Structural investigations on electrodes - electrolytes systems for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell applications

Sentencas: We identified the conditions for electrode layer synthesis in respect with porosity, composition, and mean grain size.
Titulo: Structural investigations on electrodes - electrolytes systems for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell applications
